message.body: Did you figure out a key for that hot jam?
Are they playing tonight? I'm just double checking the key now
It's a little low for me, but on the very edge of my range so it wouldn't have to be too much higher
Yeah, in stinkytown. If you can sing it in anywhere between b flat and d then we're in business, I think. Want to try and figure it out tomorrow or sunday?
I have to go to new ulm to sing at a wedding tomorrow but I could probably do it on Sunday. When works for you?
Between the afternoon and the evening
I don't work Sunday so whenever you want is a good time.
Mmk, I'll get back to you. I'm going to a movie tonight but maybe after. When do they play and where?
Blarney 10-2. Look for the drunk guy.
